headline: Crown Castle Announces Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call Details
summary: HOUSTON, Jan. 21, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Crown Castle Inc. (NYSE: CCI) ("Crown Castle") plans to release its fourth quarter 2025 results on Wednesday, February 4, 2026, after the market closes. In conjunction with the release, Crown Castle has scheduled a conference call for Wednesday, February 4, 2026, at 4:30 p.m. eastern time. A listen only live audio webcast of the conference call, along with any supplemental materials, can be accessed on the Crown Castle website at https://investor.crownc
